name: Citizen ID
description: Important identification documents of Vietnamese citizens, issued by the Public Security Agency, with the function of identifying the identity and basic information of each citizen.

name: Passport
description: A government-issued identification document that allows a citizen to leave a foreign country and re-enter his or her home country.

name: Household register
description: Legal document issued by the police to each household in Vietnam, recording information about the residence and members of the household.

name: Driving license
description: Legal documents issued by competent authorities in Vietnam, allowing individuals to operate motor vehicles such as cars and motorbikes on public roads.
